      "acceptanceCriteria": "FEA software used by all three analyst teams must operate under a documented quality management system with version control and audit trail.",
      "rationale": "All three FEA platforms (Abaqus 2021, Ansys Mechanical 2022 R2, and the FDA in-house Abaqus installation) are operated under ISO 9001-compliant QMS environments. Version numbers and patch levels are recorded in TR-NAG-2024-CB-003. Required and achieved levels are both Gradation 2; factor is satisfied."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
