    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors have been assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed their required credibility level. One factor (Test conditions) achieves Gradation 2 against a required Gradation 3, reflecting the single-configuration ASTM F1717 test campaign. This gap is accepted because the COU is explicitly scoped to compression-bending only, the model influence and decision consequence are both Medium, and the quantitative validation metric E/uval is well below 1.96 for all three QoIs. The overall credibility evidence is sufficient to support an Accepted decision for the intended use.",
